{"tid":883714,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"『加息加租』差估署：租金連升8月📈","createTime":"2018-10-31T04:51:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T05:46:18.000Z","uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7f7c16b371169a783fa383a82a1517b9d52ddfc3","tid":883714,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:51:17.000Z","msg":"差估署：9月樓價指數跌1.44% 租金連升8月<br />\n關閉<br />\n2018/10/31 10:24 留言    沽空   股價<br />\n <br />\n差餉物業估價署資料顯示，今年9月全港私人住宅樓價指數按月跌1.44%至388.8，是連續兩個月下跌；當中，A、B及C類單位(面積99.9平方米或以下)跌1.43%；D及E類單位(面積100平方米或以上)跌1.3%。<br />\n<br />\n租金方面，9月私人住宅租金指數按月升0.56%至197.8，連升8個月。<br />\n<br />\n今年首三季，樓價指數累升10.24%；租金指數升5.49%。(ac/u)"},{"pid":"306db18b2311d0f6cedcd73e1e9326841c9f8ea1","tid":883714,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:52:02.000Z","msg":"私人住宅售價指數在連升28個月後，第二次錄得跌幅。對上一個高位為本年7月，指數報394.8。中小型單位住宅樓價指數9月份為391.9，按月跌約1.43%，至於大型單位住宅樓價指數9月份為327.5，按月跌約1.30%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef37e6937a58aafa57a476977473bbe510ffff12","tid":883714,"uid":103921,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:52:34.000Z","msg":"差估署跟貼CCL，淡淡點解釋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212dbb8015e687829a7f5293446d7a3526f34e9c","tid":883714,"uid":68097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:53:55.000Z","msg":"剛需由買樓轉去租樓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c42bfb4c447645632414049ec06d44d06b7a880","tid":883714,"uid":75877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:55:42.000Z","msg":"龍1<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4fc4fc78fe6fdb6ed7e36bd175f3b93716192fe","tid":883714,"uid":28245,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef37e6937a58aafa57a476977473bbe510ffff12","tid":883714,"uid":103921,"like":2,"di